        "description": "Reynolds number, flow coefficient, and head coefficient must be confirmed equivalent between validation experiments and COU operating points to within ±5%."
      },
      "rationale": "Reynolds number (range 12,000–85,000), flow coefficient, and head coefficient all confirmed equivalent between validation and COU operating points within ±3%. Geometric similarity confirmed by CMM measurement. Achieved level 4."
