        "justification": "Placeholder offset rationale (Phase 2.5 v0.5.11 corpus regen) for 'Numerical code verification' factor shortfall on this Accepted decision. The W-AR-02 rule's intent is to flag Accepted-despite-shortfall findings that are NOT documented; structurally well-formed but not substantively meaningful. Real-world V&V 40 cases (e.g., Nagaraja et al. 2024 §4) record the offsetting evidence here."
